---
title: Quick Spiced Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Toss with Dill-Parsley Mayo & Crispy Shallots
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their chicken? This one gets a generous coating of our punchy Aussie spice blend before it crisps up in the pan until golden. Finish it off with a bed of roasted veggies (that'll take barely any effort to whip up) and top it off with a sprinkling of crispy shallots for an outstanding pairing of flavours – without the sweat and tears.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*

